### === AUTH ===

### Register
POST https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "New User", "email": "new@test.com", "password": "test123" }

### Login as Admin
POST https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@test.com", "password": "admin123" }

### Login as Analyst
POST https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "analyst@test.com", "password": "analyst123" }

### Login as Viewer
POST https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "viewer@test.com", "password": "viewer123" }

### Profile (paste your token below)
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer <paste-token-here>

### === TRANSACTIONS ===

### Create Transaction (Admin only)
POST https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 3000, "type": "income", "category": "salary", "description": "April salary" }

### List all transactions
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer <any-token>

### List with filters (income only)
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/transactions?type=income&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer <any-token>

### List with filters (expense only)
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/transactions?type=expense&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer <any-token>

### Filter by date range
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/transactions?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer <any-token>

### Filter by category
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/transactions?category=salary
Authorization: Bearer <any-token>

### Search
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/transactions?search=salary
Authorization: Bearer <any-token>

### Get single transaction by ID
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/transactions/<transaction-id>
Authorization: Bearer <any-token>

### Update Transaction (Admin only)
PUT https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/transactions/<transaction-id>
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 3500, "type": "income", "category": "salary", "description": "April salary (updated)" }

### Delete Transaction (Admin only)
DELETE https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/transactions/<transaction-id>
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

### === DASHBOARD ===

### Summary (Analyst/Admin only)
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer <analyst-or-admin-token>

### Category Breakdown
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/dashboard/category-breakdown
Authorization: Bearer <analyst-or-admin-token>

### Monthly Trend
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/dashboard/monthly-trend
Authorization: Bearer <analyst-or-admin-token>

### Recent Transactions
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/dashboard/recent
Authorization: Bearer <analyst-or-admin-token>

### === USER MANAGEMENT ===

### List all users (Admin only)
GET https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/users
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

### Change user role (Admin only)
PATCH https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/users/<user-id>/role
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "analyst" }

### Toggle user status (Admin only)
PATCH https://fintrack-be.vercel.app/api/users/<user-id>/status
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
